comments: LaVine (CHI) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he moves to imminently guard Haliburton (IND).
Beverley (CHI) is imminently exiting the lane within three seconds.
Turner (IND) is in the paint for less than three seconds when he is imminently exiting.
Hield (IND) brings his arm toward Beverley's (CHI) path as Beverley rolls following the pick, and marginal contact occurs as they disengage.
Haliburton (IND) brushes LaVine's (CHI) right arm while retracting a slight forearm from his side and marginal contact during the driving shot attempt.
LaVine (CHI) avoids bringing both hands to the ball during his dribble.
Turner (IND) is drawn into the air on the pump fake toward LaVine (CHI) and marginal body contact occurs with LaVine's side on the perimeter.
Mathurin (IND) does not maintain a legal guarding position on LaVine (CHI) during his jump shot attempt, and there is foot contact that affects LaVine's ability to return to the floor.
DeRozan (CHI) exits the paint within three seconds.
Turner (IND) is firming up into Beverley's (CHI) path when foot to foot contact occurs within the frame of Turner's body.
Beverley (CHI) release the in-bounds pass within five seconds.
DeRozan (CHI) is turning slightly as he establishes screening position and marginal contact occurs with McConnell (IND) as he moves around the screen.
Turner (IND) contests the jump shot attempt and avoids making contact with Vucevic's (CHI) arms.
